(350, 325, 'Currency conversion rate', 'Specify rate X, where 1 USD = X in shop currency.<br/>The shipping cost is always returned in US Dollars. So if the store uses a different currency for payments, you need to specify a conversion rate to convert the shipping cost returned by the shipping service into your store''s currency. If the same currency is used, leave this set to 1.', 'en'),
