(9, 8, 'PayPal Payflow Link', 'Credit/Debit card or PayPal', '', '', 'Accept Visa, MasterCard®, American Express, Discover and PayPal payments on your site by connecting a PayPal-hosted checkout page with your own internet merchant account. Customize the page to look like the rest of your site and make sure customer transactions are secure.', '', 'en'),
